  "detailed_description": "<strong>Immersive 6 degree of freedom 1000kmh+ high speed flying experience</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950460/extras/8dbd08cc0b3d32c02184b57fe52e1220.poster.avif?t=1726593625\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950460/extras/8dbd08cc0b3d32c02184b57fe52e1220.webm?t=1726593625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950460/extras/8dbd08cc0b3d32c02184b57fe52e1220.mp4?t=1726593625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Tunnel: Over 2000 different possible styles</strong><br><br>The tunnel is procedural random generated from many possible different styled units, forming huge amount of potential combinations, giving new experience and mood each play!<br><br><br><strong>Supports PC & Meta Quest 2 VR</strong><br><br>Minimal discomfort with control mechanism of “steering by tilting your body”:<br>Tilt L/R to steer L/R, Tilt backward to steer up, Tilt forward to steer down.<br>You can even feel the gravity when you steer up and down!<br><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><br>You will be driving through an infinitely long sci-fi tunnel as fast as possible to try to escape from a plasma blast chasing behind you. Collect energy spheres for life-saving speed boosts. Survive as long as you can!<br>The background music's pace is linked to the speed of the spacecraft, to maximize your speed induced excitement!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Immersive 6 degree of freedom 1000kmh+ high speed flying experience</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950460/extras/8dbd08cc0b3d32c02184b57fe52e1220.poster.avif?t=1726593625\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950460/extras/8dbd08cc0b3d32c02184b57fe52e1220.webm?t=1726593625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950460/extras/8dbd08cc0b3d32c02184b57fe52e1220.mp4?t=1726593625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Tunnel: Over 2000 different possible styles</strong><br><br>The tunnel is procedural random generated from many possible different styled units, forming huge amount of potential combinations, giving new experience and mood each play!<br><br><br><strong>Supports PC & Meta Quest 2 VR</strong><br><br>Minimal discomfort with control mechanism of “steering by tilting your body”:<br>Tilt L/R to steer L/R, Tilt backward to steer up, Tilt forward to steer down.<br>You can even feel the gravity when you steer up and down!<br><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><br>You will be driving through an infinitely long sci-fi tunnel as fast as possible to try to escape from a plasma blast chasing behind you. Collect energy spheres for life-saving speed boosts. Survive as long as you can!<br>The background music's pace is linked to the speed of the spacecraft, to maximize your speed induced excitement!",
